# Design Patterns

## Color Palette

### Primary Colors
- **Base Background**: Deep purple/navy (#2d2b40 or similar) serves as the main app background
- **Primary Accent**: Vibrant purple (#6c5ce7 or similar) for buttons, selected items, and interactive elements
- **Secondary Accent**: Teal/mint (#66d9c9 or similar) for secondary actions, progress indicators, and accents

### Supporting Colors
- **Card Background**: Pure white (#ffffff) for content cards and modals
- **Dark Mode Card Background**: Near-black (#1e1d2b) for dark mode cards
- **Text - Primary**: Near-black (#212121) on light backgrounds
- **Text - Secondary**: Gray (#6b7280) for secondary information
- **Text - Light**: White (#ffffff) on dark backgrounds and colored buttons
- **Notification/Accent**: Red (#e74c3c) for notification indicators and important badges

## Typography

- **Font Family**: Clean sans-serif typeface (SF Pro, Inter, or Outfit)
- **Hierarchy**:
  - **Heading Large**: 24-28px, Semi-bold (600)
  - **Heading Medium**: 18-20px, Semi-bold (600)
  - **Body Text**: 14-16px, Regular (400)
  - **Secondary/Caption**: 12-13px, Regular (400)
