## Component Styling

### Cards & Containers
- **Border Radius**: Consistent 8-12px rounded corners across all cards and UI elements
- **Card Elevation**: Very subtle shadow (2-4px blur, 10-20% opacity)
- **Inner Content Padding**: Consistent 24px padding inside cards
- **Card Spacing**: 16-20px gaps between adjacent cards
- **Section Separation**: 24-32px vertical spacing between major sections

### Buttons & Interactive Elements
- **Primary Button**: Filled purple with white text, slightly rounded corners (8px)
- **Secondary Button**: Light purple or white with purple text/border
- **Hover States**: Subtle darkening (5-10%) on hover
- **Active Elements**: Highlighted with primary purple background and white text
- **Icons**: Thin stroke (1.5-2px), minimalist style, consistent with text color

### Navigation & Sidebar
- **Sidebar Width**: Appropriately proportioned (64-80px collapsed, 240-280px expanded)
- **Selected Item**: Purple background highlight with white icon/text
- **Hover Item**: Subtle background color change (5-10% lighter/darker)
- **Icon Size**: Consistent 20-24px height
- **Vertical Spacing**: 16-20px between nav items

### Form Elements
- **Input Fields**: Light gray/lavender background (#f5f5ff or similar), 8px border radius
- **Input Focus**: Subtle purple border/glow on focus
- **Checkboxes/Toggles**: Purple when active, gray when inactive
- **Dropdowns**: Clean white background, subtle shadow on open

## Visual Patterns & Details

### Data Visualization
- **Charts & Graphs**: 
  - Purple and teal as primary colors
  - Pastel secondary colors when needed
  - Clean, rounded edges on bars/elements
  - Light grid lines (10-15% opacity)
  - Smooth transitions between data points

### Spacing System
- **Base Unit**: 4px as base unit
- **Component Padding**: Generally multiples of 8px (8, 16, 24, 32)
- **Micro-spacing**: 4-8px between closely related elements
- **Macro-spacing**: 24-32px between major sections

### Special Effects
- **Avatars/User Images**: Circular with subtle border
- **Status Indicators**: Small colored dots (4-6px)
- **Notifications**: Small, bright purple circles with white numbers
- **Progress Elements**: Smooth, rounded indicators using the teal-purple gradient

### Layout Principles
- **Card Grid**: Clean, aligned cards with consistent spacing
- **Whitespace**: Generous breathing room between elements
- **Alignment**: Strong left alignment for text and content
- **Hierarchy**: Clear visual hierarchy through size, weight, and color

### UI "Feel" Elements
- **Modernity**: Clean, minimal, flat design with subtle depth
- **Professionalism**: Balanced color usage, not overly playful
- **Focus**: High contrast for important data/actions
- **Breathing Room**: Generous whitespace creates a calm experience
- **Consistency**: Unified styling across all components 